snippet.title: Combat Beans Early Access - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
The early access is finally here! Get the game and play now! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1717080/Combat_Beans_Total_Mayhem/

Join the discord - https://discord.com/invite/6vcRDyfVzr
Twitter (X?) - https://twitter.com/CombatBeansGame
Steam Community - https://steamcommunity.com/groups/PeanutBrains

12-Bean arena shooter with Free for all and King of the hill game modes. Level up your bean and unlock a ton of cosmetics to show off. Comes with a single player time trial challenge mode as well with unique challenge unlocks. More content added frequently, check the roadmap!

I`m a solo dev and this is my first game. Be gentle :`)
